itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雖然對大陸人真係無咩好感 但都係對事不對人 佢地有做賤格野先會憎佢地 人地遭遇咁不幸既野 連隻腳都無埋 有D人把口仲咁毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一日上連登咩 講太多小心比人加埋你入五毛名單添啊</blockquote><br />\n有同理心就要比人加入五毛名單 咁我寧願比人加飽佢都唔想無左自己人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同咩理心姐, 係佢企太出比車轆, 求仁得仁, 點解要同情？</blockquote><br />\n唔講以為佢俾香港人推出馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696025a58e27ed3667a90f8f13ce343c96bd0201","tid":456252,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 見骨 我屌你老豆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正呀喂"},{"pid":"afb15c224e0901bbe91cbaa3b6e54c5ede3b76af","tid":456252,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大撚把香港人企出去啦<br />\n你地係咪未出過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩出事果個唔係香港人啫<br />\n不過你班連登仔唔出街<br />\n唔怪你</blockquote><br />\n得你係<br />\n果D唔係香港人"},{"pid":"8f042f83d228e17fbbcb1782303e69b0ebb70749","tid":456252,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"有眼耳口鼻就係美女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45ce38a7f74f73cd73f301ec3bd7fb98b909aca","tid":456252,"uid":26816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"#8樓唔見咗<br />\n究竟post左d咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64deb86eb1800509e8e4902554bd6dd8657d7928","tid":456252,"uid":20951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>#8樓唔見咗<br />\n究竟post左d咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無打格既斷腳圖"},{"pid":"a825f2bc41fc4d6cb79a257ca4a097ebe6b9b8f1","tid":456252,"uid":54654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"睇相好肥喎老友"},{"pid":"d896a95a8be6440479ef59038ca37e4245277601","tid":456252,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一睇就知肥婆啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">修你老母美長腿咩</span></blockquote><br />\n笑撚死 擺明大媽級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  乜鳩野審美黎"},{"pid":"7624c20d55c08bc664f1addbb2fdd14b0c647d70","tid":456252,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n有同理心就要比人加入五毛名單 咁我寧願比人加飽佢都唔想無左自己人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同咩理心姐, 係佢企太出比車轆, 求仁得仁, 點解要同情？</blockquote><br />\n乜撚野求仁得仁 佢特登比車轆既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎香港就係一心想比人切撚左隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用下個閪腦先講野好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係人都知企出馬路就有機會畀車撞㗎喇<br />\n佢明知都仲企出去<br />\n依家咪得償所願畀車車斷腳囉</blockquote><br />\n架巴士護欄都撞彎埋呀柒頭<br />\n你老母出街俾車車死老豆出街冧牌招責死我第一個賀你萬事勝意<br />\n好像賀若蓮喪子咁賀</blockquote><br />\n如果企喺護欄入面，至少唔駛斷腳，自己on9企出馬路俾車夾斷腳</blockquote><br />\n結論真係自己on9 希望佢下次企返入d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6740587ef5af16f7a3fe534a51b1f8d96b4f8097","tid":456252,"uid":17628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n如果企喺護欄入面，至少唔駛斷腳，自己on9企出馬路俾車夾斷腳</blockquote><br />\n你話佢企路中心就話姐 用你邏輯既話平時出街唔著避彈衣有日比變態佬掃射都係自己On9 係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n噏乜鳩，唔著避彈衣出街有無做錯先，企出馬路又有無做錯先？屌你咁都要拉埋嚟比喻係咪on9"},{"pid":"013aac4e355de5bb5018a8905143fa71d104c4f8","tid":456252,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"甜？ 邊撚度甜呀睇過"},{"pid":"273f215ca653fb4721f80876debf59875973075e","tid":456252,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9de68a9d5b4c91acca1a608ba323fa2d155b6b7","tid":456252,"uid":3194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"好慘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n殘廢支那妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跛住過下半世呢柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf695798b020c1d07fce2ac1571777d27ef1401","tid":456252,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁既閪樣叫甜美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2"},{"pid":"e5f5d02814ea1b53929a863a9af2d98b6d639c7c","tid":456252,"uid":3194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:57:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無同理心架？人地來旅行咋.如果第日你地去其他國家旅行被人車死又點</blockquote><br />\n哦，希望有果一日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就唔怕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bf21023dd2f42754c3ef724c8942305ee0957d","tid":456252,"uid":3194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T06:00